Name: Fuel Cell Dispatch Manual

Caption.String: Copy Schedules from Battery Dispatch Schedules
Use the Copy Schedules button to overwrite the weekday and weekend schedules with the manual dispatch schedules from the Battery Dispatch page.
The manual fuel cell dispatch option allows you to choose when to run the fuel cell, and for systems with batteries, when to charge the battery from the fuel cell.
